            <h1>Installing on Linux</h1>
            <p>Running Pak on Linux is supported by building from source code.
            Please see instructions at <a href="source.html">Building from Source</a>.</p>

            <a id="running"></a>
            <h2>Running Pak</h2>
            <p>You can run pak via:</p>
            <pre class="ui code segment">
pak
</pre>
            <p>To get all the options for Pak, read the man page via:</p>
            <pre class="ui code segment">
man pak
</pre>or get the command help via:
            <pre class="ui code segment">
pak --help
</pre>
